namic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/121105/', '', 'Micafungin, Amphotericin B, Miconazole, Oteseconazole, Flucytosine, Anidulafungin', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Sipuleucel-T, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Ropeginterferon alfa-2b, Interferon alfacon-1, Sargramostim, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, More', 1767369485);
